data.description: Convenient location, large private lot, and incredible layout in the tranquil neighborhood of Meadow Ridge! All 4 bedrooms are located on the main level, with an additional bonus room over the 2 car attached garage of this 2083sf home. Vaulted ceilings and an open concept contribute to the spacious feel of the interior. The primary suite boasts a large bedroom, 3 closets, a soaker tub and double vanities with cultured marble tops. The additional 3 bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home. New carpets throughout the main level and white plantation style blinds on all windows. So many assurances - freshly pumped septic, original owners, termite bond, architectural shingles and full gutter system. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, tile backsplash, recessed lighting, a pantry and stainless-steel appliances INCLUDING refrigerator. The laundry room is tucked off the kitchen for convenience. Enjoy proximity to parks, schools, dining, shopping, and medical care. No HOA!
